songs.title: Serena
songs.lyrics:
Get strapped up bitch it gon get bumpy
Can’t trump me,Donald Duck’s want that bread,always responding to em quite bluntly
Im grumpy,cat in the hat,also got a gat,bullet to the back
You don’t know jack,boy get smacked,bodies in a sack,This the predator pack,too big for your boots,haven’t quite a hoot,in it for the loot,want some diamonds maybe a suit,whale a hoe like pearl,nigga fuck that lil bitch earl,2018 nigga,want that Grammy,fuck Beyoncé and jay,now the pot swirl,don’t mind me,dear dear diary,you can find me,i ain’t no kind fiend,lil bitch just watch me assign these goons,see you soon,maybe monday noon,don’t forget the tune,tune of the loons,damn
